reviews.text:
Absolutely amazing mix. It's simple, straight to the point, and great for a beginners DIY juice. Forest Mix is the perfect mix of berries to nail down the mixed berry lemonade feel without feeling overwhelming, and LA lemonade really adds that extra lemon punch.&#xD;
&#xD;
If you are a beginner, definitely try out this recipe. Hell, make sure to try it out even if you arent.
